text: The Shopinas.com Lady Clickers were a women's volleyball team that played in the Philippine Super Liga (PSL). The team was owned by Air21 Global, Inc. and was formed from the remnants of the disbanded Generika Lifesavers. ==Roster== For the 2015 PSL All-Filipino Conference: {| class="wikitable" style="text-
